title: Did Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez Wear a $7,600 Ensemble to the State of the Union Address?
subtitle: The new U.S. House member's critics can't seem to decide whether she has too much money or too little.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: U.S. Rep. Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez wore a $7,600 ensemble to the State of the Union address.
